						<div class="postbody">Since you want the format to define everything under the sun, how is this format better than any XML format which is actually extensible, and emulators can support as little or as much of the crap bundled with the ROM as they want? Sure your format encompasses a lot (whether this is good is debatable), but it's very static and rigid. It looks like a nightmare to implement, so have you taken a poll of who will use it before you invest much more time defining it?</div>

